                "description": "Divide batter evenly among 12 cupcake liners. Bake at 375 for 12-15 minutes."
            },
            {
                "description": "Microwave chocolate chips and whipping cream for 20-30 seconds, then give it a good stir. It should melt. Once the cupcakes are cooled, dip the tops in the ganache. Let set before frosting."
